name: Valkyrie - Disgaea
description:
My loras are SFW/NSFW friendly - though her petite nature could be an issue as NSFW

works with most styles - weight could be 0.5 - 0.7 - trained for 768 (may have better results)

to keep close to her old design try any of these - or put in Neg (changing appearance/outfit)

For appearance

Valkyrie, for appearance - short green pixie cut, headband, pointy ears,

  • you can change hair and skin color more or less

for attire

VAtt, bare shoulders, brown belts, armored thigh boots, bike shorts ,midriff, beltbra, belt buckle

  • would add, belt bracers, in prompt and put gloves in NEGS

  • can more or less change the color of gear
